net.cloud.gfx.focus

Class SingleFocusHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.gfx.focus.SingleFocusHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FocusHandler

    public class SingleFocusHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements FocusHandler
    A focus handler which acts as a single link. This handler will keep track of the focus of a single thing, and can have a previous and next handler in line.
